content: What would people who know me say I'm good at?
Am I a good listener? Do I offer a listening ear that is more focused on the needs of others, as opposed to my own?
What can I do right now that my future self will thank me for?
What am I struggling against that I can simply release?
How do the people who surround me reflect who I am?
When was the last time I massively over-delivered on something? Why did I work so hard?
How much time do I spend looking for things I can't find?
When was the last time I stepped out of my comfort zone?
